Collect Rooms and Spaces - Collect rooms and MEP spaces in the Revit document.
Use "Rooms to Zone" node to convert them to Honeybee zones.

Collect Rooms and Spaces - Collect rooms and MEP spaces in the Revit document.

Use "Rooms to HBZones" node to convert them to Honeybee zones., Rooms to HBZones - Create Honeybee zones from Revit Rooms or MEPSpaces.
This node currently ONLY collects geometrical data from Revit. In the future it will import constructions, materials and MEP data (e.g lighting power density).

content.description:
Honeybee connects Revit and DynamoBIM to Radiance and OpenStudio (EnergyPlus) for daylight and energy simulation.

This version supports point in time daylight and sunlight hours analysis. Annual daylight analysis will be added soon.
